16
00:00:41,355 --> 00:00:45,295
Assuming that stronger penguins breed more successfully,

17
00:00:45,665 --> 00:00:48,434
we plan to compare their body size.

18
00:00:48,435 --> 00:00:51,005
When we catch a penguin,

19
00:00:51,105 --> 00:00:53,104
- we measure five things.
