please repeat them and write them down.

26
00:01:08,855 --> 00:01:10,485
- Okay.
- I'll tell you in order.

27
00:01:10,785 --> 00:01:13,255
(I should write it down well.)

28
00:01:13,425 --> 00:01:15,124
Doctor, I should capture a penguin.

29
