(With its exposed skin, its body heat is transferred directly.)

49
00:02:08,745 --> 00:02:09,845
That's interesting.

50
00:02:11,785 --> 00:02:13,614
It can't move when you hold it by its tail.

51
00:02:13,615 --> 00:02:17,385
(The penguin is captured in a special bag.)

52
00:02:20,125 --> 00:02:22,524
(The research team takes the egg from its nest as well.)

53
00:02:22,525 --> 00:02:24,825
Did you take the egg because other animals could steal it?

54
00:02:25,295 --> 00:02:26,295
Yes.

55
00:02:27,135 --> 00:02:28,765
(A skua)

56
