(After looking around, )

57
00:02:32,005 --> 00:02:34,875
(it approaches the egg and snatches it quickly.)

58
00:02:36,635 --> 00:02:40,004
Other animals could take the egg while the penguin is absent.

59
00:02:40,005 --> 00:02:41,014
Yes.

60
00:02:41,015 --> 00:02:44,085
(The egg must be collected as other animals might steal it.)

61
00:02:44,385 --> 00:02:47,154
Careful with the precious egg.

62
00:02:47,155 --> 00:02:48,155
(The research team must not let its guard down.)

63
00:02:48,485 --> 00:02:50,685
- Okay.
- Yes.

64
