102
00:04:07,435 --> 00:04:08,894
(They seem like a pair of good brothers.)

103
00:04:08,895 --> 00:04:10,295
- Thank you.
- You'll be able to write well.

104
00:04:11,135 --> 00:04:12,135
Gosh, it's...

105
